{"tid":2401889,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"衞生署開位抗疫 只聘退休警  月薪高達13.5萬 被轟「拉封鎖線都未掂」","createTime":"2021-02-10T05:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T07:20:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"75c8e08d2a8b8b3a4ea7b81c3b3059f400ea8d39","tid":2401889,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/NBBNA5DLL5BSPL2FOJB3IW6YKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FNBBNA5DLL5BSPL2FOJB3IW6YKU%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQs0BU04RHr%2BP31d0xuhNw0M%3D&h=78d23cba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FNBBNA5DLL5BSPL2FOJB3IW6YKU%2F&h=32da5f07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/NBBNA5DLL5BSPL2FOJB3IW6YKU/</a><br />\n<br />\n衞生署開位抗疫 只聘退休警 <br />\n月薪高達13.5萬 被轟「拉封鎖線都未掂」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】作為控疫主要部門的衞生署事事慢半拍，近日疫情大幅放緩，才「醒覺」要增聘人手處理各類流行病學追蹤等工作，卻離奇地只請退休警員。本報發現，衞生署最近就多個新增職位招聘，但只限退休警務人員，涵蓋職級由普通警員上至高級警司，最高月薪13.5萬元兼享15%約滿酬金。區議員質疑，政府旨在逐步擴大警隊的公權力及影響力，若他日更多職位專請警察，抗疫就難有人權、自由可言。<br />\n<br />\n綜合警隊招聘網頁及消息人士。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其餘五個職位，共通點是沒指明隸屬。。。。。。。。。。。。。最低級的則是調查員助理，退休警員或以上職級就可應徵，月薪3.6萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pgBss7AwRjul_HnmO-LK_S4ZWwY=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L3F5XR2UGNEYBJZERWZVBFPTRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpgBss7AwRjul_HnmO-LK_S4ZWwY%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL3F5XR2UGNEYBJZERWZVBFPTRQ.jpg&h=01ccefe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警隊近期抗疫行動表現受質疑；圖為早前警員在深水埗封區時狂奔拉封鎖線。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n余德寶質疑旨在擴警權<br />\n<br />\n過去一年，衞生署多次招攬現職或退休紀律部隊人員，參與口岸登記、撤離行動、突襲封區等工作，當中又以警員為主，今次可謂疫潮爆發以來首度為退休警「度身訂做」合約職位。油尖旺區議會副主席、公民黨余德寶指出，去年2月康美樓撤離行動時，警員穿「伊波拉」保護衣在疫廈大外圍駐守，近日深水埗封區拉封鎖線時又「跑過龍」，表現貽笑大方，「拉條封鎖線都未掂，點做流行病學追蹤？」<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，若上述職位不需醫學知識，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署稱，為保障公共衞生，一。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aaZyhyvRfTIMRmjjefaGn5iy3pI=/2551x582/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YKN7GM7YEBDJXLOTM2URMRQQDI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaaZyhyvRfTIMRmjjefaGn5iy3pI%3D%2F2551x582%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYKN7GM7YEBDJXLOTM2URMRQQDI.gif&h=281bbc11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手機用戶請按此放大圖表"},{"pid":"ed48ba05ca2eeb8584a4312300629645884b0d27","tid":2401889,"uid":294618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"信黨"},{"pid":"caf3e6f2b2d747aa350cf169be77315637347a91","tid":2401889,"uid":55868,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:32:51.000Z","msg":"對大陸公安好唔公平！！<br />\n強烈要求只用大陸退休公安"},{"pid":"2f7d12fd4fd4aab38f44e3ec18ca0fbd43e6cf06","tid":2401889,"uid":314496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211b4e4f2a619ef4578bad17919b9dc17be86e10","tid":2401889,"uid":52946,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:00:41.000Z","msg":"輸送利益到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258f3718c19a0e792f07b52a5911d410a4fe677f","tid":2401889,"uid":245552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"211b4e4f2a619ef4578bad17919b9dc17be86e10","tid":2401889,"uid":52946,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:00:41.000Z","msg":"輸送利益到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:05:32.000Z","msg":"黎緊呢d野只會愈來愈多愈來愈唔會掩飾"},{"pid":"2197c3837c509c703a5159c70096700379e981b1","tid":24018